  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 266ee5624740d8b43b24e535e8e2b780, type: 3}
  m_Name: TutorialBook
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  textLines:
  - text: "The UI tutorial goes over the basic functions of the book menu, equipping
      abilities, find information provided by each item/ability and navigating through
      other parts of the book menu. \n\nThe majority of the tutorial will take place
      within the actual menu itself, then show how the menu gets updated with a notification
      prompt with a book icon on the UI."
  - text: "The movement tutorial takes you into the a new tutorial area that goes
      over the basic controls for movement within the game. You will be required
      to pickup star items to proceed through the tutorial and proof of completing
      the tutorial. \n\nOnce you collect the last star, you will be brought back
      to the level."
  - text: This tutorial will take place in another scene to show you the main interactions
      with the NPCs within the game, saving them, and interacting within the town.
  - text: 'This tutorial will go over the controls behind the Charge Dash ability
      and what are the different scenarios it can be applied to. '
  - text: 'The UI tutorial goes over the basic functions of the book menu, equipping
      abilities, find information provided by each item/ability and navigating through
      other parts of the book menu. '
  - text: This tutorial will discuss the door function within the game, how to interact
      with it and counts as a door.
  npcName: Narrator
